      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRONT MAN (4) won again in an impressive display after leading them home to make it two on the bounce, scoring by one length (19.33) at this track over 350m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can continue on with his winning form. FLYAWAY JACK (3) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. Missed the frame latest (20.28) when eighth over 366m at Capalaba in a Restricted WIN. Can feature with the right run. EXHIBIT (2) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a second place finish (16.87) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ZARA'S COMET (6) is very honest and looms as a strong top-three hope again.",
